| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2024-3411 — Recovery Inhibition (blacksuit)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 82d52b1e-6041-560b-9d17-0dd9ce3a073f"
